        <dd class="most-popular-title"><a href="http://www.theatlantic.com/health/archive/2014/05/theres-no-such-thing-as-a-slut/371773/" data-omni-click="inherit">There's No Such Thing as a Slut</a></dd>
                <dt>6</dt>
        <dd class="most-popular-title"><a href="http://www.theatlantic.com/magazine/archive/2014/11/understanding-stalin/380786/" data-omni-click="inherit">Understanding Stalin</a></dd>
